channel.title: Grrrrrrrrrrrrr
channel.description: Well heres my story , i wake up today and start to play some p servers. And i some how jeesh i should make my own. So i go to moparscape forums and look up how to make my own. I succesfully made one off the Fr33Sc4p3 Pkz Base. Everything is working alright EXCEPT i can't add anything to the server , i tried adding defenders , changing the name , etc. NOTHING WORKS.... is it my compiler? WTF I've tried 30+ tutorials , none of them work on my server and i've spent 7hrs+ straight. Can SOMEONE HELP ME. Im like sooo frustrated right now!
